						"description": "Upload an audio or video file to detect emotions. The API will automatically extract audio from video files and return the detected emotion.\n\n**Supported Formats:**\n- Audio: .wav, .mp3, .flac, .aac, .ogg, .opus, .m4a, .aiff, .amr, .wma\n- Video: .mp4, .mkv, .webm, .avi, .mov, .mpg, .mpeg, .flv, .3gp, .ts, .f4v\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"emotion\": \"happy\"\n}\n```"
					},
